    <title>机器学习-凸优化</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/10/25/article-title/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/10/25/article-title/</id>
    <published>2017-10-25T06:47:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-10-28T04:33:05.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">printf(&quot;hello Markdown!&quot;)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>凸函数(convex)：  </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(\mathbf{y}) \geq f(\mathbf{x}) + \nabla f(\mathbf{x}) ^ {T} (\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x})</script></blockquote><p>强凸函数(strongly-convex)：   </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(\mathbf{y}) \geq f(\mathbf{x}) + \nabla f(\mathbf{x}) ^ {T} (\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x}) + \frac{m}{2}||\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x}||^2</script></blockquote><p>L-Lipschitz   </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(\mathbf{y}) \leq f(\mathbf{x}) + \nabla f(\mathbf{x}) ^ {T} (\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x}) + \frac{L}{2}||\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x}||^2</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\Leftrightarrow |\nabla f(x) -\nabla f(x) < L||x-y|| |</script></blockquote><p>平方损失(square-loss):  $y \in \mathbb{R}$   </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)) = \frac{1}{2}(y_i-h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta))^2</script><p>其中在线性回归中 ，$h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta) = \theta^T \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i$)     </p></blockquote><p>对数损失(logistic loss):   $y  \in \{-1,1\}$      </p><blockquote><p>$l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)) = log(1+exp(-y_i h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)))$   </p></blockquote><p>一阶导数(one order of diff of square-loss)       </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\nabla_{\mathbf{x}_i} l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)) = \frac{\partial l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta))}{\partial \theta} = (y_i-h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)) \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i)</script></blockquote><p>二阶导数(two order of diff of square-loss)</p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\frac{\partial \nabla_{\mathbf{x}_i} l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta))}{ \partial \theta } = \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i)^T</script></blockquote><p>— 求二阶Hessian矩阵的特征值:   </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i)^T \mathbf{z} = \lambda \mathbf{z}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">(\Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) ^T \mathbf{z})\Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) = \lambda \mathbf{z}</script><p>因此得到：   </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\mathbf{z} = k \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \quad k \neq 0</script><p>代入上式得到：   </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\lambda = \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) ^T \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \geq 0</script></blockquote><p><span style="color:blue">s所以平方损失(square-loss)是凸函数，若$\Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) ^T \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \geq c ,c&gt;0.$那么平方损失(square-loss)是强凸函数</span></p>]]></content>
    
